387:    "summary": "FBE 'recreation succeeded but only app-of-apps + 1 service' is an ArgoCD finalizer deadlock, not a branch/render bug. The slot's Applications are stuck Terminating (deletionTimestamp + resources-finalizer); ArgoCD logs 'Skipping auto-sync: deletion in progress' and the owning ApplicationSet cannot recreate a same-named app-of-apps.",
388:    "root_cause": "A chronically failing PostSync seed hook (alarmengine POST /v1/assets/seed -> HTTP 500) leaves its Job with argocd.argoproj.io/hook-finalizer; on a later delete the cascade wedges on that Job -> child Application can't delete -> app-of-apps can't delete -> ApplicationSet can't recreate. Symptom: only the leftover app-of-apps + the wedged child show; ApplicationSet conditions are all green (render/generation is fine), which DISPROVES the developer's usual 'I broke my branch's vpp-config' render hypothesis but NOT branch runtime-deployability. RESOLVED 2026-06-04: after clearing the deadlock, the FBE auto-rebuilt and alarmengine seed returned 204 (not 500) with secrets present -> the seed-500 was the missing secret-provider-kv (a deadlock symptom: secretprovider child wasn't deployed), NOT the developer's branch content. Branch exonerated by live evidence. Lesson: the chronically-failing seed that wedged the finalizer was itself downstream of the half-deployed state, so a clean recreate fixes both.",
389-    "fix": "Diagnose: kubectl -n argocd logs argocd-application-controller-0 | grep <slot> | grep 'deletion in progress'; check .metadata.deletionTimestamp + finalizers. Unblock (Tier-1, voltex-scoped, literal names only): strip the stuck hook Job finalizer (kubectl -n <slot> patch job <seed-job> --type=merge -p '{\"metadata\":{\"finalizers\":[]}}'), force-delete zombie pods, watch 'objects remaining' drain; ApplicationSet auto-recreates (no pipeline rerun). Last resort gated: strip resources-finalizer child-then-parent. THEN Track 2: clearing the deadlock is necessary-not-sufficient -- capture the alarmengine log at seed time to pin the 500 (branch image/appconfig vs missing secret-provider-kv SecretProviderClass) or it recurs. NEVER: destroy pipeline 2629 as rollback; argocd app delete --cascade (can't reach the k8s Job finalizer); -l/--all/wrong-ns; touching <slot>-monitoring.",
