title: "FBE Fix And Knowledge Discipline"
summary: "Safe execution gates, anti-patterns, and vault writeback rules for FBE incident response."
description: "FBE fix safety gates: fix-gate preconditions, name-guarded destruction, polling discipline, pipeline-2412 pre-rerun checks, the destroy-2629-is-not-rollback anti-patterns, and vault writeback; load before prescribing or running any FBE remediation."
